\pard\f0\fs28 Annual herbs. Leaves pinnatifid, glandular-punctate, alternate or opposite. Capitula small. Involucral bracts 5-8, in one row or with 2-3 small outer bracts, free. Receptacle concave, without scales. Florets (3-)4(-5), one ligulate and female, the others tubular,hermaphrodite. Achenes 4-angled, pubescent. Pappus of 8 scales.
\par

